                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Griscom</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-10-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 23, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Reports that he is informed by the minister of finance and leader of the Chamber
                    of Deputies that the Brazilian tariff law will not be altered during the
                    Congress now in session. It is intended to postpone for a year the consideration
                    of the tariff already begun.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
